  "description": "<p><strong>Role: Operations Assistant Manager [Deployment & Reporting]</strong></p><p><strong>Industry: Education</strong></p><p><strong>Location: Tiong Bahru</strong></p><p><strong>5 Days (3 weekdays & 2 weekends) | Weekdays: 10.20am - 7.20pm [On-site] Weekend: 7.00am – 5pm [WFH]</strong></p><p><strong>Salary: $2,800 - $3,200</strong><br /></p><p><strong>Requirement:</strong></p><ol><li><strong>At least Degree / Diploma in any discipline</strong></li><li><strong>Possess relevant experience</strong></li><li><strong>Proficiency in MS Office, Zoom, Google Drive</strong></li></ol><p><strong></strong><br /><strong>Key Responsibilities:</strong></p><p><strong>Teachers & CSO Deployment</strong></p><ul><li>Plan and manage relief processes across branches for Teachers & Customer Service Officers -Track Attendance of Teachers & Customer Service Officers</li><li>Develop communications packages for teachers (e.g. Infographics, etc)</li><li>Design simple collaterals in accordance with brand marketing guidelines</li><li>Assist with scheduling and tracking of teacher assessments, appraisal, etc</li></ul><p><strong>Data-tracking & Manpower Resource Management</strong></p><ul><li>Plan and manage relief processes across branches for Teachers & CSOS</li><li>Oversee Teacher Allocation across all branches</li><li>Measure adherence to leave policies and implement measures to encourage adherence Manage relief data sheets</li><li>Deliver monthly report on key data points tracked by team</li></ul><p><strong>Oversee Relief Roster</strong></p><ul><li>Find relief teachers</li><li>Consolidate a list of relief, freelance relief classes taken monthly and inform HR</li></ul><p><strong>Assist with forecasting of recruitment needs of the following groups of teachers:</strong></p><ul><li>Relief, Adjunct, Part-time and Freelance</li></ul><p><strong>Data-tracking for Operations</strong></p><ul><li>Manage key data sheets for Operations needs</li><li>Deliver monthly report on key data 